# Framework Example Rules

- Examples must demonstrate the same `SerialSession` behavior.
- Keep examples minimal.
- Avoid framework-specific API divergence.
- Update examples when public API changes.
- Angular examples are included in this Issue.
- React / Svelte / Vue.js examples are handled in separate Issues.
